\par\plain {\f0\fs22 The whole point of this post is to point out the course\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s message that there is ultimately nothing to fear. That was Jesus\u8217\'92s message, the Urantia book\u8217\'92s message, (Unreasoned fear is a master intellectual fraud practiced upon the evolving mortal soul), and the Course in Miracles message. The creation of the Supreme Being is a messy business here on earth. It is like making sausage. But nothing from an eternal perspective is in danger.}
